---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base>
  <div class="intro">
    <h1>Lucas Beillo</h1>
    <p class="muted mono" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">Data analyst · BI, visualization &amp; data quality · A Coruña, Spain</p>

    <p>
      I'm a data analyst with 4+ years building ETL/ELT pipelines, running data-quality processes, and
      shipping BI dashboards that hold up under real use. Recent work: modelling 300k+ cadastral records
      in PostgreSQL/PostGIS, and running scraping and QA pipelines across 50+ e-commerce platforms that
      cut manual work by 60%.
    </p>
    <p>
      Day to day that's Python, SQL, Power BI, Tableau, and dbt. A background in environmental engineering
      and GIS is a plus, not the focus — it just means spatial and sensor data don't scare me.
    </p>
    <p>
      On the side I build Life Tracker, a personal data warehouse that pulls my own data from five sources
      into a single analytical model — an excuse to run a full pipeline end to end.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside work, I run. More on that soon.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Recent projects</h2>
    <div class="card-list">
      <div class="card" style="display: block;">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
          <span class="card-title">Life Tracker <span class="mono muted">(healthkit)</span></span>
          <span class="card-meta">in development</span>
        </div>
        <span class="card-desc">
          Personal data warehouse aggregating five sources into one analytical model.
          Pipeline: Python → DuckDB → dbt → Flask API → React dashboard.
        </span>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">Python</span>
          <span class="tag">DuckDB</span>
          <span class="tag">dbt</span>
          <span class="tag">Flask</span>
          <span class="tag">React</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a class="card" href="https://recolle-v02.vercel.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;">
          <span class="card-title">Recolle</span>
          <span class="card-meta">live</span>
        </div>
        <span class="card-desc">
          Civic-tech app for geolocated incident reporting, used to verify municipal cleaning-service
          quality — photo, category, and GPS, in real time. Mobile-first, in production.
        </span>
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="tag">React 18</span>
          <span class="tag">Leaflet</span>
          <span class="tag">Firebase</span>
          <span class="tag">Python</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2>Stack</h2>
    <p class="mono muted">SQL · Python · Power BI · Tableau · dbt · PostgreSQL/PostGIS · QGIS · Git</p>
  </div>
</Base>
